# pattern.java
package siva7;
import java.util.*;
public class patterns {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		// TODO Auto-generated method stub
		int n;
		Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
		n=sc.nextInt();
		for(int i=0;i<=5;i++){
			
			for (int j=0;j<=n;j++){
				System.out.print("*");
			}
			System.out.println();
		}

	}

}
